    <item>
      <title>
        Thomas Jefferson Said &#34;Government That Governs Least Governs Best.&#34;
      </title>
      <link>https://www.factopolis.com/person/rand-paul/2012-03-20/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2013 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://www.factopolis.com/person/rand-paul/2012-03-20/</guid>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <blockquote>
          Jefferson said that, &ldquo;Government is best that governs least.&rdquo;
        </blockquote>
        <p>
          <cite>— Rand Paul, speech on 2013 federal budget</cite>
        </p>
        <h4>Claims:</h4>
        <dl>
          
            
            <dt>
              <a href="https://www.factopolis.com/claims/jefferson-government-that-governs-least-governs-best/">Thomas Jefferson Said &#34;Government That Governs Least Governs Best.&#34;</a>
            </dt>
            <dd>
              <h5>The Truth:</h5>

              It&rsquo;s often misattributed to him, but he never said it.
            </dd>
          
        </dl>
        
      ]]></description>
    </item>
    
